sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Svelte)
    participant A as App (Wails Binding)
    participant PM as PlanningManager
    participant PA as PlanAccess
    participant R as Repository (Git)

    Note over C,R: SaveDayFocus with OKR IDs and Tags
    C->>A: SaveDayFocus({date, themeIds, notes, text, okrIds, tags})
    A->>PM: SaveDayFocus(access.DayFocus)
    PM->>PM: Validate date non-empty
    PM->>PA: SaveDayFocus(day)
    PA->>PA: extractYearFromDate()
    PA->>PA: GetYearFocus(year) [read existing]
    PA->>PA: Upsert entry (themeIds, okrIds, tags all persisted)
    PA->>PA: Sort by date
    PA->>PA: WriteJSON(calendar/{year}.json)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PA-->>PM: nil
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: Client-side: OKR picker in day editor dialog
    C->>A: GetThemes()
    A-->>C: []LifeTheme (with objectives, key results)
    C->>C: Render ThemeOKRTree with checkboxes
    C->>C: User checks KR checkbox
    C->>C: Auto-select parent objective + theme (ancestor propagation)
    C->>C: Collect selected OKR IDs into okrIds[]

    Note over C,R: Client-side: Tag picker in day editor dialog
    C->>A: GetTasks()
    A->>PM: GetTasks()
    PM-->>A: []TaskWithStatus
    A-->>C: []TaskWithStatus
    C->>C: Extract unique tags from all tasks
    C->>C: Render tag pills (toggle) + tag text input (create new)
    C->>C: Auto-derive text field from selected tags
    C->>C: Collect active tags into tags[]

    Note over C,R: Combined save with all fields
    C->>A: SaveDayFocus({date, themeIds, text, notes, okrIds, tags})
    A->>PM: SaveDayFocus(access.DayFocus)
    PM->>PA: SaveDayFocus(day)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PA-->>PM: nil
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil
